Phase 1.2: Source Control Setup
Create Git repository.
Learn:
Initial commit
Commit messages
Branches (optional)
Suggested commits:
Initial Solution Setup
Added Core Library
Added NUnit Test Project

QA Lesson: Every change should be traceable.


Phase 1.3: Project Planning Documentation
Create simple documents:
Project Scope
Requirements List
Validation Rules
Future Enhancements
Example:
Reservation must have name
Reservation date must be future
Party size must be greater than zero
Duplicate reservations not allowed
QA Lesson:
Requirements drive testing.

